Package nl.weeaboo.vn.script

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IScriptContext
    Context-specific part of a script environment.
    IScriptEnv
    Container for global scripting-related state shared between all IScriptContext objects.
    IScriptEventDispatcher
    Interface for scheduling pieces of code to run on the main thread of a script context.
    IScriptExceptionHandler
    Handles exceptions from script code.
    IScriptFunction
    Java wrapper around a script function.
    IScriptLoader
    Loads script resources.
    IScriptThread
    Java wrapper around a script thread.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ScriptException
    Exception thrown by a script.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    ScriptFunction
    Annotation to mark methods that should be made available to the scripting environment.
